definition: Jia County in Yulin 榆林[Yu2 lin2], Shaanxi

sentences.english: The temple, which lies on the banks of the Yellow River in Jiaxian, Shaanxi Province, is supported by a stone column that is more than 20 meters high.
sentences.chinese: 香爐寺位於陝西省佳縣境內的黃河崖畔。

sentences.english: In the last part, it explores the internal diversity of Jia County's dialect.
sentences.chinese: 第五部分，分析佳縣方音的內部差異。

sentences.english: It was drafted at Shenchuanpao, Chiahsien County, northern Shensi.
sentences.chinese: 宣言是在陝北佳縣神泉堡起草的。

sentences.english: The authors used the meteorological observation data of Jiaxianin nearly 34 years to test the models.
sentences.chinese: 用佳縣近34年的氣象觀測資料對模型進行檢驗。
